claim.claim-text:
A system (100) comprising:
a flow inlet conduit (102);
a primary conduit (104) branching from the flow inlet conduit for delivering flow to a set of primary nozzles;
an equalization bypass valve (106), EBV, that connects between the flow inlet conduit and a secondary conduit (108) for delivering flow to a set of secondary nozzles, wherein the EBV is connected to be controlled to apportion flow from the flow inlet conduit (102) to the secondary conduit (108); and
a secondary equalization valve (114), SEV. that connects between the flow inlet conduit (102) and the secondary conduit (108), wherein the SEV is connected to be controlled by drain pressure, PD, to apportion flow from the flow inlet conduit to the secondary conduit.
